</p>
<p>And of course, make sure you have a <code>return</code> statement in front of all of
this! Let's enjoy our hard work by echo'ing the method below: <code>$myShip</code>,
arrow, <code>getNameAndSpecs</code> then the open and close parenthesis so PHP knows
this is a method, not a property by that name.</p>
